property_headline: Designer apartment with balcony & tranquil outlook - Oversized 81sq design - fully furnished
property_description: This spacious (fully furnished) apartment is exceptionally private, modern and ideal for those seeking convenience with lifestyle appeal. Overlooking the park, this bright and airy apartment features generous proportions, quality fittings and represents an excellent lifestyle location close to all the local attractions plus transport points. Light-filled living/dining area's which flow seamlessly to the balcony - Ideal for entertaining or relaxing. Entertain in style with the Modern kitchen with stainless steel appliances including dishwasher, gas cook top & seated breakfast bar / island. The Master bedroom is spacious with direct balcony access plus separate study nook and AC. Modern security building and facilities; In/outdoor swimming pool and well-equipped gymnasium. Apartment features: - Stylish high quality modern finishes - full furnished pad - Excellent North West aspect with open plan living and dining area - Modern gourmet kitchen with breakfast bar + quiality appliances - Oversized bedroom with access to balcony - AC throughout - This security building also includes an indoor swimming pool, a spa, sauna and full equipped gymnasium to help resident obtain a healthy lifestyle.

property_headline: Two-level home with large balcony in 'Sonoma' building. 6 month lease.
property_description: A two-level home with a large balcony in the well-regarded 'Sonoma' building, this is a contemporary space designed by award-winning architects Allen Jack + Cottier. With an oversized feel and unique layout, it fuses innovative design with quality finishes in a tasteful result. 6 month lease. Highlights * Spacious 2-level modern design * Opening to dual balcony settings * Natural light & airflow throughout * Double bedroom w/ built-in robe * Modern Caesarstone, kitchen, gas * Internal laundry, intercom entry * Residents' outdoor swimming pool * Top location 100m to Waterloo Park * Walk to Danks St & Green Sq hubs
